title: Bob Marley and The Wailers 1980-05-30
description:
Here is another nice bootleg. Check my account for more classic bootlegs.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)


This is from the Liberated Bootleg "Uprising At Hallenstadion" Godfatherecords.  It is my second upload on this site.  I got it from another tracker, and I did not see it on this site, so I thought I would share.  Hope you like it.  Sound quality A+++
*************************************



Bob Marley & The Wailers - Liberated Bootleg "Uprising At Hallenstadion" Godfatherecords.
Live at Hallenstadion, Zurich, Switzerland 30th May 1980

This is from a brilliant soundboard recording, one of the best sounding Bob Marley and the Wailers boots (in my opinion)

Lineage (for me): CD > EAC (WAV) > TLH (FLAC level 8) > DIME

Setlist (69:57):
1. Zimbabwe
2. Natty Dread
3. I Shot The Sheriff
4. No Woman, No Cry
5. TalkinÂ’ Blues
6. We And Dem
7. Lively Up Yourself
8. Jamming
9. Exodus
10. Redemption Song
11. War / No More Trouble
12. Kinky Reggae
13. (end of Kinky Reggae) > Get Up Stand Up 

Feel free to share this & enjoy Bob Marley and the Wailers's first concert from their final tour!
